CCID version 1.5.2 Universal installation package for macOS Sonoma (14). 

Support both Intel & Arm processors on macOS versions Mojave (10.14) and later.

This fixes an issue with Sonoma default CCID driver and Thales connected smartcard readers & tokens

It supports all the Gemplus, Gemalto and Thales readers/tokens.
 
This installer is based on the open source CCID driver and libusb, both covered by GNU LGPL 2.1.
Source code is available from:
• https://libusb.info (license: https://github.com/libusb/libusb/blob/master/COPYING)
• https://ccid.apdu.fr (license: https://github.com/LudovicRousseau/CCID/blob/master/COPYING)

